Testing out [stack edit](http://stackedit.io)

```java
Class DoStuff
	Method DoStuff(&amp;someVar as boolean out);
End-Class;

Method DoStuff()
	/* &amp;someVar */
	&amp;someVar = (1+1=2);
End-DoStuff;

Then to use it:

import STUFF:DOSTUFF;
&amp;doStuff = Create STUFF:DOSTUFF(&amp;myVar);
WinMessage(&amp;myVar);
```
Would display 'true'
```java
import STUFF:DOSTUFF;
Class DoDynamicStuff extends STUFF:DOSTUFF;
 Method DoDynamicStuff(&amp;var as boolean);
End-Class

Method DoDynamicStuff
	%super = create STUFF:DOSTUFF();
end-method;
```
